    "answer": "BDE",
    "explanation": "【핵심 용어】\n▸ OIDC IdP — OpenID Connect 기반 외부 인증 제공자\n▸ AssumeRoleWithWebIdentity — OIDC 토큰으로 임시 자격 증명 획득\n▸ 신뢰 정책 — OIDC 제공자로부터의 역할 전환 허용\n\n【정답 포인트】\n▸ B) IAM IdP 생성 → OIDC 제공자 등록 (URL, 대상, 서명 정보)\n▸ D) 신뢰 정책 구성 → auth.company.com:aud로 조건 지정 (정확한 IdP 출처 검증)\n▸ E) AssumeRoleWithWebIdentity → OIDC 토큰으로 AWS 역할 전환, S3 API 호출\n\n【오답 체크】\n(A) IAM Identity Center → AWS 관리형 SSO, 기존 외부 OIDC와 다른 패턴\n(C) sts.amazon.com:aud → AWS 서비스 조건 키, OIDC IdP 조건 아님\n(F) GetFederationToken → 동일 계정 리소스 공유용, OIDC 외부 제공자 적합하지 않음\n\n【시험 포인트】\n▸ OIDC 연동 흐름 — 외부 IdP 등록 → IAM 역할 신뢰 정책 → AssumeRoleWithWebIdentity\n▸ 조건 키 정확성 — IdP 도메인 기반 조건 (auth.company.com:aud)\n▸ Federated 인증 패턴 — 웹 애플리케이션에서 OIDC 토큰 획득 후 AWS 역할 전환",
    "en_q": "A company is refactoring applications to use AWS. The company identifies an internal web application that needs to make Amazon S3 API calls in a specific AWS account. The company wants to use its existing identity provider (IdP) auth.company.com for authentication. The IdP supports only OpenID Connect (OIDC). A DevOps engineer needs to secure the web application's access to the AWS account. Which combination of steps will meet these requirements? (Choose three.)",
    "en_opts": {
      "A": "Configure AWS IAM Identity Center (AWS Single Sign-On). Configure an IdP. Upload the IdP metadata from the existing IdP.",
      "B": "Create an IAM IdP by using the provider URL, audience, and signature from the existing IP.",
      "C": "Create an IAM role that has a policy that allows the necessary S3 actions. Configure the role's trust policy to allow the OIDC IP to assume the role if the sts.amazon.com:aud context key is appid_from_idp.",
      "D": "Create an IAM role that has a policy that allows the necessary S3 actions. Configure the role's trust policy to allow the OIDC IP to assume the role if the auth.company.com:aud context key is appid_from_idp.",
      "E": "Configure the web application to use the AssumeRoleWithWebIdentity API operation to retrieve temporary credentials. Use the temporary credentials to make the S3 API calls.",
      "F": "Configure the web application to use the GetFederationToken API operation to retrieve temporary credentials. Use the temporary credentials to make the S3 API calls."
    },
    "source": "https://www.examtopics.com/discussions/amazon/view/133261-exam-aws-certified-devops-engineer-professional-dop-c02/"
